title: PM visits Navruz Palace in Dushanbe
content:
DUSHANBE, July 02 (APP): Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif on Tuesday visited the Navruz Palace and appreciated Tajik architecture art.
Upon arrival at the Palace, the prime minister was warmly received by President of Tajikistan Emomali Rahmon and accompanied him during the visit, PM Office Media Wing said in a press release.
Later, the Tajik president hosted a dinner at the Navruz Palace in honour of the prime minister and his delegation.
